> Inside:
> ~/ai-os
>
> Create:
> .env
>
> Eventually it will contain:
> DOMAIN=3Dexample.com
>
> EMAIL=3Dyou@example.com
>
> TZ=3DAmerica/Edmonton
>
> POSTGRES_USER=3Daiadmin
>
> POSTGRES_PASSWORD=3D...
>
