>>>> Why a VPS?
>>>> The VPS is the always-on backbone of the system.
>>>> It will:
>>>>
>>>> host Hermes
>>>> expose secure endpoints
>>>> run scheduled jobs
>>>> store memory
>>>> connect to APIs
>>>> orchestrate automations
